Package: tidyvpc
Type: Package
Title: A new, flexible, powerful and efficient R package to compute VPC percentiles and prediction intervals
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2020-02-17
Authors@R: c(
      person("Olivier", "Barriere", email = "olivier.barriere@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut")),
      person("Benjamin", "Rich", email = "mail@benjaminrich.net",
