Description: The tidyvpc package makes computation of percentiles and prediction intervals fast and easy, while accounting for stratification, censoring, and binning. Using piping from magrittr, the intuitive syntax provides users a flexible and powerful method to perform Visual Predictive Checks (VPC) using traditional binning and new binless methods with Additive Quantile Regression (AQR) and LOESS prediction correction.
URL: https://github.com/jameswcraig/tidyvpc
BugReports: https://github.com/jameswcraig/tidyvpc/issues
